    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's been really well-loved and taken care of, so it's in great shape and runs like a dream. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this car is super reliable and ready for its next adventure. I've kept it nice and clean, and I'd love for someone to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
