    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-string S54B32 powerhouse. This unit is mechanically robust, having undergone critical preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure timing precision. The chassis integrity is secured with subframe reinforcement plates, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the tactile feedback expected of this M-division icon. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the drivetrain is optimized for peak performance and longitudinal stability.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
