    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, with only the occasional minor stone chip typical of responsible highway use. Inside, you'll find a clean, smoke-free environment featuring plush leather seating that shows minimal bolster wear and remains incredibly comfortable for long hauls. All interior technology\u2014including the intuitive infotainment system, backup camera, and heated seats\u2014is fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it has a documented service history, shifts smoothly through all gears, and sits on a set of high-quality tires with significant tread life remaining. It has been garage-kept and recently detailed, making it a turnkey option for any buyer looking for reliability and style.",
      "price": 34500.0,
