    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next adventure with you! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
